ReCircle AI – Complete Project Handover
Project Goal

Build a native Android application called ReCircle AI for a national-level sustainability competition.

The objective is to help users correctly identify waste, understand its environmental impact, and learn the proper way to recycle it using AI.

This is not a web app or Flutter project.

